Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spii-iike? Are you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellooooo? ...Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was starting to\Nthink you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize this\Nis last minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've decided on a\Nquick trip to the Gem Cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am on an urgent\Nmission to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,some facetted iridescence\Nfor my new design
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't think of anypony\NI'd rather have along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,than my favorite basket\Nholder slash body guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.61,0:00:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha? Oh. Hey, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if you\Nhaven't been listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... of course I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but just to be sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,could you say it all again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] I was saying that I planned\Non visiting the Gem Cave and--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [bustling music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nyou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bit of\Na late start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and those gems won't\Npick themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But the real question is.. which\Nbasket do you want to hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The smaller one, right?\NAh ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Sorry Rarity, can\NI take a rain check on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The... Gem Cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Sounds great,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but I need to get to the\Npost office before noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! All right.\NVery funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, you'll get the\Nbigger basket and I sh-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For as long as we've\Nknown each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike has never turned down an\Nopportunity to join me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his favorite place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ideally, you catch\Nthe gems, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And for a trip to the post\Noffice of all places!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should move closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And why would Spike need to\Ngo to the post office at all!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He sends mail by BREATHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathing, darling!\NBreath mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Applejack, if\Nyou're going to fill in,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you COULD make an ATTEMPT\Nto hold the basket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the way Spike would!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And how's {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for one thing, Spike\Nknows how to keep things {\i1}quiet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so as not to waken the BATS!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,AND he usually\Nfollows me closely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so no gem ever\Ntouches the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, Spike's been\Nfollowing you closely
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,since he got\Nto Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And in case you\Nhadn't noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I AIN'T SPIKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,ACTUALLY, APPLEJACK,\NI HAD NOTICED!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... hi, Rarity.\NWhat's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides my mane? Well, that\Nis a question for Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, Spike isn't here. I\Nthink he's at the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:04:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again{\i0}? What is it with\NSpike and the post office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, what's\Ngoing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike declined my\Ninvitation to the Gem Cave
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I intend to\Nfind out why!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. That doesn't\Nsound like Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you two have\Nsome sort of fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}fight{\i0}?\NGoodness, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What in Equestria\Nwould we fight about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had arguments\Nwith friends before
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and they can put a real\Nstrain on friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, certainly, but\NI think I'd remember
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,if we had an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you didn't\Nrealize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could\Nhave done something
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that unintentionally\Nhurt his feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I didn't\Nrealize what I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,how would I know what I\Nhave done when I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly would explain his\Nbehavior. I must apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pfft that's hardly the\Npoint! Poor Spikey Wikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS calls for a\NGRAND gesture!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Good talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's a big crate\Nof stuff you're mailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not mailing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you pushing\Nit into the post office?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I didn't realize\NGriffins worked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Ponyville\NPost office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! [giggle] No! I don't\Nwork here, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the official mail\Ncarrier of Griffonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabby Griffon.\NNice to meetcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Yes, well! These things\Naren't for sending...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're for\Napologizing to Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Spike was just here.\NHe went to go make us a-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect! It'll give\Nme a chance to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} stand there\Nand tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if I hit the right\Napologetic notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Napologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, I don't see\Nwhy that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [sappy music] ♪{\i0}\NAnd that is why I simply\Ncannot bear the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of having hurt yoooou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though I don't\Nknow what it is that I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to know\Nthat it doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm prepared to do\Nanything to make it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry,\Ndear. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I said.. that sure\Nsounds genuine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course it sounds\Ngenuine! It IS genuine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I'm working on\Nmy apology to you, Spike...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I could be\NMORE genuine I mean... [gasp] SPIKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [sappy music] ♪{\i0}\NOh, Spike, I am so\Nsorry! Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU HAVE TO FORGIVE ME!\NI don't know what I did
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or why you're mad at me;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,just please say you\Nforgive me! [blubbering] Pleeease!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh, what are\Nyou apologizing {\i1}for{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everypony\Nkeep harping on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Don't YOU know..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm not mad at\Nyou about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But-but I don't understand.\NIf you're not upset with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,why in Equestria would you\Nrefuse to go to the Gem Cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, because I\Nhad other plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[crash]\NWith me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. You\Ntwo know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabby and I are\Nsort of pen pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! There was this whole\Nthing where I pretended
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to get a cutie mark because\NGriffons don't get cutie marks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so Princess Twilight had Spike\Nsend a bunch of letters off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to Griffonstone about\Nthe first Griffon ever
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to get a cutie mark, which\NI really didn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabby wrote back explaining\Nthings, and after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we just started\Nwriting back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out we have\Na lot in common!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We both come from cultures
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that don't have the\Nfriendliest of reputations...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,AND we're both in the\Nmessage-sending business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh!\N[splat]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure wish {\i1}I{\i0} could\Nsend scrolls with my breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ha yes..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand why you\Ndidn't come to the Gem Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a friend in\Ntown is a rare treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, since you're\Nbusy today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we can do something\Ntomorrow. Fabric shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you {\i1}love{\i0} to\Npick out the colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Er. Actually, now that there's a\NGriffon at Twilight's school,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabby's here all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Gruff asks\Nfor a lot of updates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,about how Gallus\Nis doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Speaking of which,\NI'd better get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fly with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right.\NYou two fly along..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Spike and I can do\Nsomething some other...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [sad music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot decide which shade\Nof purple is the most royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's the PINK!\NHow will I ever choose!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah. Too bad Spike's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he could help\Nyou narrow it.. down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a good sounding\Nboard, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [upbeat music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you bring the pin\Ncushion a little closer, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose now that Spike's\Nalways so busy with Gabby,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just now realizing\Nhow much his presence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,has meant to me\Nover the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even closer, darling. I\Ndon't want to prick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit\Neverything feels a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,'less than' without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, darling, it's no use.\NThank you for trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just accustomed\Nto the help
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of a small, highly\Nattentive dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should let Spike\Nknow how grateful you are
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for everything\Nhe's done for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I am sorry, Spike! I\Ndidn't mean to frighten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity? What are\Nyou doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I realize it's\Nlate, or rather early,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have a surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just couldn't\Nwait to share it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Gem Crevasse\Nof the Crystal Mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only accessible\Nonce a year
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought a little day\Ntrip would make a wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for all the\Nhelp you've given me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,over the years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. But I'm supposed to meet\NGabby today for her rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, there's\Nalways next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? I'll\Njust write her a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Rarity, you\Nweren't kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gem Crevasse\Nwas amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be snacking on\Nthese for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabby: Hey, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabby! You won't believe\Nwhere I went today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think I\Nwill! I got your scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Gem Crevasse\Nsounds a lot better
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,than doing my rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It was\Ndefinitely better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta get back\Nto Griffonstone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have to tell me all\Nabout the Crevasse tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunt] Thanks again, Rarity.\NWhat a great day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Start from\Nthe beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,because I wanna\Nhear everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to get to\Nthe Crevasse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to climb\Nacross a rope bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because the air's\Ntoo thin to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That is amazing!\NThen what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[thud]\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no apology\Nnecessary, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I was just\Nlooking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You were? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I just\Nacquired.. these!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Passes to Power\NPonypalooza!? For today!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm! I know we just\Nwent to the Crevasse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel I've barely\Nscratched the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of expressing my\Ngratitude for all you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.. Of course I wanna go, but\Nthat'll be two days in a row
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't hung out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha... are you kidding? It's Power\NPonypalooza. You have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And.. now you'll have two\Nthings to tell me about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Come on,\NRarity, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [melancholy music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew. Are my claws sore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! I had no idea\Nhow much walking there is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at a Power Pony\Nconvention!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I told Gabby\Nwe'd hang out tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I might need the\Nwhole day to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! I know\Nwhat you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you could, uh just\Nsend her another note.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. I think maybe\Nyou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I might\Nneed to spend tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,putting my hooves\Nup as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't counted on\NPower Ponypalooza
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,being quite so draining,\Nbut I thought we might
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,spend the day\Nrecuperating together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Ogres\N& Oubliettes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know how\Nmuch you enjoy it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and this seemed like\Nthe perfect opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to teach\Nme the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike? I got your note.\NI figured I'd come by
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,before my rounds with a bowl\Nof energizing turnip soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can Princess Shmarity use\Nher Shield of the Coiffure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to defend herself\Nfrom the purveyor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of poor color\Ncoordination?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. She can try...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Success! Shmarity's\Nshield holds against
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the Green-Eyed Monster's\Nattack and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, Gabby.\NWe were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your scroll said you were too\Ntired to do anything today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess you were just too\Ntired to do anything with me..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no!\NThat's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can come with you on\Nyour rounds right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think\Nso, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just handle the\Nrounds on my own from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Princess Shmarity\Nuses her Prismatic Beam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to change that poor\Nmonster's color
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to a more pleasing\Nshade of purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think,\NSpike? Solids or prints?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Prints, I guess. You already\Nhave a lot of solid colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are so\Nright. Prints it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So nice to have\Nyou back, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I hope you're able\Nto reconcile with Gabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure she\Ndoesn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I quite enjoyed our\Nday together, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Spike!\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I've never seen\NSpike this sad before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know\Nwhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.. Yes, well, perhaps\Nhe's still just tired
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,from Power Ponypalooza.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think\Nthat's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... I suppose\Nit's {\i1}possible{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it could have something\Nto do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[cough] Gabby not wanting to spend\Ntime with him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I thought the two of them\Nwere hanging out all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They were! Honestly, it\Ntook everything I had
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to convince him to spend\Nany time with {\i1}me{\i0} at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But between crystal\Ngem crevasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Pony conventions and\Na marathon game of O&O,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to get\Nsome time in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you made\Nsure he didn't have any time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to spend with Gabby at all..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Pfft! I\Ncertainly did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose I may have\Nmonopolized him a teeny bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just grown so used to\Nhaving Spikey-wikey around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't prepared for how much\NI'd miss him when he wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendships change,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but just because Spike\Nmade a new friend
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean he\Nstops being yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but now I\Nhave to share him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which I suppose I'll\Nhave to get used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Right after I fix\Nthis mess I've made!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!? Is all this\Nstuff for Spike again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be easier\Nto just give it to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here to apologize.\NActually, more to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of this stuff\Nisn't for Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the evidence\Nagainst ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Evidence? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For my acts of\Nutter selfishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the items\NI used to lure Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,into spending as much\Ntime with me as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They are? You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously I'm\Napologizing to Gabby
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so the two of you can renew\Nyour friendship, Spike...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now please, even if\Nyou can't forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you simply must\Nforgive... SPIKE!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I actually owe\N{\i1}you{\i0} an apology too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You apologize a lot..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh. I wish I didn't need to,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but the more time you\Ntwo spent together,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the more I missed\Nmy time with Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and the more I used every means\Nat my disposal to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You really missed\Nspending time with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say, after not\Nhanging out with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why.\NYou're kinda awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And.. I know what it's like\Nto miss that now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you think maybe we\Ncould start hanging out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you'd\Nlike some company
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,on your rounds\Nright now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure would!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful! I can't tell\Nyou how pleased I am
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that the two\Nof you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,..reconciled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose Twilight is right.\NFriendships do change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Spike and I\Nwill always be friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and I {\i1}can{\i0} get used\Nto sharing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oo ah ooh ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I just didn't\Nwant to drop another one
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and wake the bats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling. Catching the gems\Nis what the basket is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Wow. You two need\Nto be a lot quieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! How wonderful\Nto see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Gabby and I\Nhad a great day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll always still\Nwant my Rarity time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh! So that's how it works...
